sketch.compiler.parser

Class StreamItParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • sketch.compiler.parser.StreamItParser

  • public class StreamItParser
extends java.lang.Object
    A light wrapper around the main parser. Allows us to do things like preprocess input files before parsing them, uniformly handle IO errors, and so forth.
    Author:
    Chris Jones
